{"word":"G2372 - θυμός - thymós - thoo-mos' - Fierceness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θυμός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>thymós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>thoo-mos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Fierceness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"உக்கிரம், கோபம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. passion, angry heat"},{"paragraph":"2. glow, ardor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G2380 - θύω - thýō - thoo'-o/2380\">G2380</a>; <i>passion</i> (as if <i>breathing</i> hard): - fierceness, indignation, wrath. Compare <a href=\"#/G5590 - ψυχή - psychḗ - psoo-khay'/5590\">G5590</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1760 - ἐνθυμέομαι - enthyméomai - en-thoo-meh'-om-ahee/1760\">G1760</a>, <a href=\"#/G1761 - ἐνθύμησις - enthýmēsis - en-thoo'-may-sis/1761\">G1761</a>, <a href=\"#/G1937 - ἐπιθυμέω - epithyméō - ep-ee-thoo-meh'-o/1937\">G1937</a>, <a href=\"#/G1938 - ἐπιθυμητής - epithymētḗs - ep-ee-thoo-may-tace'/1938\">G1938</a>, <a href=\"#/G1939 - ἐπιθυμία - epithymía - ep-ee-thoo-mee'-ah/1939\">G1939</a>, <a href=\"#/G2372 - θυμός - thymós - thoo-mos'/2372\">G2372</a>"}]}